data.description: Welcome home for the Holidays! Located minutes from the Village of Pinehurst and across from the Pinehurst Lake and Pinehurst No. 3, this stunning Pandich Construction home has it all.  Upgrades include 2 en-suite bedrooms, hardwood floors throughout, a bonus room, a custom kitchen with LG stainless appliances including a gas range,  separate wall ovens and beautiful granite, a walkout basement, extra paved parking, a fenced in yard, and an abundance of storage.   The primary bedroom is on the main floor with a huge walk-in closet.
